(Recommendation 1: Launch a 30-day activation campaign in Kano and Oyo focused on) Tj
T*
(first-purchase incentives, onboarding messages and follow-up reminders for new customers.) Tj
T*
(Owner: Head of Growth. Expected outcome within 60 to 90 days: raise Kano's 30-day conversion) Tj
T*
(rate from 25.86% and Oyo's from 30.16% toward the current Lagos benchmark of 41.78%,) Tj
T*
(improving the return on acquisition spend. This recommendation is based on Query 1.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Recommendation 2: Create a seller quality review for high-revenue, mid-rated products,) Tj
T*
(starting with the electronics category and sellers attached to the top 10 revenue products.) Tj
T*
(Owner: Head of Seller Operations. Expected outcome within 60 to 90 days: reduce the risk) Tj
T*
(that fast-growing electronics sales create customer dissatisfaction, while moving more) Tj
T*
(revenue from the mid-rated group into the high-rated group. This recommendation is based on) Tj
